    Class Description
    CarPanel
    This class provides the GUI for a program that stores and displays service orders for an auto shop

    The driver class for a program that stores and displays service orders for an auto shop

    This class tests the add method of three types of list that extend LinkedList
    MakeList
    A LinkedList that holds objects that implement ServiceOrderInterface As ServiceOrderInterface objects are added to the LinkedList they are sorted in order based on the make, model, and year
    OrderList
    A LinkedList that holds objects that implement ServiceOrderInterface As ServiceOrderInterface objects are added to the LinkedList they are sorted in order based on the order number
    OwnerList
    A LinkedList that holds objects that implement ServiceOrderInterface As ServiceOrderInterface objects are added to the LinkedList they are sorted in order based on the owner name
    ServiceOrder
    This class contains the information needed to store service orders for an auto shop
    ServiceOrderManager
    This class creates 3 LinkedLists that contain ServiceOrderInterface objects In order to send and receive information from a GUI to display, add, and delete orders For an auto shop Each LinkedLsit sorts the objects based on different criteria

    Test for Service Order Manager
